{"questionId":"21935923","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Consider the function defined by&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>P</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced></mrow><mrow><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mi>Q</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced></mrow></mfrac></math>, where&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>≠</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>≠</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p>attempt to cancel factors and substitute <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><munder><mi>lim</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></munder><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><munder><mi>lim</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></munder><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><msup><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></mrow><mrow><msup><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced></mrow></mfrac></mfenced><mo>=</mo><munder><mi>lim</mi><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>→</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></munder><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn